verbose_text: Validation of the RNA-seq data shows that HFFF2s treated with iC and iRAS derived sEVs show an increase in the mRNA expression levels of cell-cycle regulators CDKN2A, CDKN1A, components of the SASP, and integrin beta3 subunit (ITGB3), which regulates senescence (XREF_FIG G and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY E).
evidence: levels of cell-cycle regulators CDKN2A, CDKN1A, components of the SASP, and integrin
